description: With a hint of Carolina and Texan tradition, Billy Hannah's Pulled Pork & More offers a unique flavor to the city of San Antonio; delivered and cooked in a custom made smoker. Providing excellent customer service and a menu that gives YOU the authority to create a dish to satisfy your BBQ cravings, Billy’s Pulled Pork will become your new favorite! Our seasoned pulled pork is slowly cooked to perfection with our signature BBQ sauce. Enjoy our slow smoked brisket, spare ribs, or smoked chicken, and choose from an array of tasty side dishes.Book US for your next catering event!
name: Billy Hannah's Pulled Pork & More
